@Test public void testName() { /*assertEquals(expectedResult, actualResult); assertTrue(someCondition); assertFalse(someCondition); */}
Class: AtomicInitializer, Method: get
Description: /*** Returns the object managed by this initializer. The object is created if
* it is not available yet and stored internally. This method always returns
* the same object.
*
* @return the object created by this {@code AtomicInitializer}
* @throws ConcurrentException if an error occurred during initialization of
* the object
*/
